         <abstract id="aspace_a850ca429eb6f4596050a3ff2bac061d">Correspondence, and campaign materials relating to William J. Walker's unsuccessful campaign as Republican candidate for mayor of Albany, New York in 1937.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
